name: vsalert
tagline: Alerting service - AngularJS reusable UI component
body:
### Description
Simple AngularJS service which implements the alert system. This component depends on only the AngularJS.

1. Four levels (success, info, warning and error)
1. Lightweight (only one service with CSS)
2. Depends on only the AngularJS
